# Gunster, Yoakley & Stewart

Gunster, Yoakley & Stewart, P.A. (known as Gunster) is a full-service law firm based in West Palm Beach, Florida, where it was founded in 1925.
Gunster maintains 13 offices in the Florida cities of Boca Raton, Fort Lauderdale, Miami, Naples, Orlando, Jacksonville, Tallahassee, Tampa, Stuart, Vero Beach, and Palm Beach.
Gunster represents clients in corporate law, real estate, litigation, land use, healthcare, estate planning, and government affairs.
